PRIMARY OBJECTIVE OF POSITION
Controls and handles all uniforms in accordance with the standard
_____________________________________________________________________
RESPONSIBILITIES
Meets and exceeds customer expectation by ensuring department provides Yes I Can! service and teamwork
• Provides value-added service to customers by doing whatever reasonable and possible to meet or exceed customer expectations
• Communicates effectively with customers, co-workers, and supervisors
• Demonstrates teamwork by cooperating and assisting co-workers as needed
• Handles difficult situations effectively
• Meets Yes I Can! service standards
• Performs other duties as required to provide Yes I Can! service and teamwork
Maintains the appearance of hotel employees by performing repairs to uniforms
• Issues and completes alternations on employee uniforms
• Mends and repairs uniforms as needed, recommend replacements to supervisor if repairs needed are too great
• Control the uniform handling
• Issues uniform to new staff
• Control all uniforms handled back to the housekeeping when staff is resigning
• Control and keep record of all uniforms handled back for cleaning
• Check, count and record all uniforms going to the laundry /dry cleaning
• Check , count and record all uniforms returned from laundry / dry cleaning
• Repair of guest cloths upon request
Improves the appearance of the hotel by repairing linen as necessary
• Removes and records reject linen from inventory
• Inventory all uniforms as required
• Keep working area clean at all times
• Mop floors, clean shelves in the uniform room when required
Adheres to hotel policies and procedures
• Attends work on time as scheduled in flexible manner towards Hotel needs
• Follows hotel grooming and dress standards
• Minimizes safety hazards by following all safety rules and procedures
Requirements
• Fluency in English
• Experience from a similar position or equivalent
• Strong interpersonal skills
• Highly motivated, enthusiastic and innovative
• Outgoing, dynamic and sales focused
• Yes I Can Attitude
